/* Table: "CON_RejectReasonCode" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_RejectReasonCode"
(
"RejectReasonID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ReasonType" INTEGER,
"RejectReason" VARCHAR2(1000),
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
constraint PK_CON_REJECTREASONCODE primary key ("RejectReasonID")
);
